<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA49">
<l>makiḻala koṉṟēpōṉ māṟumpal yākkai</l>
<l>nekiḻa muyalkiṟpārk kallāṉ – mukiḻvirinta</l>
<l>cōtipōṟ ṟōṉṟuñ cuṭarpoṉ ṉeṭumuṭiyem</l>
<l>mātikāṇ pārkku maritu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for those who exert themselves so that [their] bodies are so</l>
<l>emaciated that [they] alter to the likeness of a single makiḻ-seed,</l>
<l>it is difficult for those who [want to] see our First cause with the high</l> 
<l>crown of glowing gold that appears like a blooming radiance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
